snippet.title: TY the Tasmanian Tiger Steam Trailer 1
snippet.description:
Struth mates! Would ya believe the great Aussie hero TY the Tasmanian Tiger is making his way to PC with his first classic adventure? Now remastered in glorious HD and with a new batch of effects to make it sparkle shinier than a ridgy-didge Thunder Egg!

Follow us on Facebook for the latest info!
